## POST /kyc/documents/:id/retry

Rejected document ko dobara upload karo. **Max 3 attempts** allowed hain.

**Path Param:** `id` — document ID (GET /kyc/status response mein milta hai)

**Ye API sirf tab kaam karti hai jab:**
- `status = 'rejected'`
- `canRetry = true` (attemptsLeft > 0)

### Frontend Logic:
```
if (doc.status === 'rejected' && doc.canRetry) {
  // Retry button dikhao
  // POST /kyc/documents/{doc.documentId}/retry
}
if (doc.attemptsLeft === 0) {
  // "Contact Support" dikhao
}
```

### Success Response (200) — same as /submit:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "documentId": 3,
    "documentType": "DRIVING_LICENCE",
    "status": "auto_verified",
    "message": "DRIVING_LICENCE verified successfully"
  }
}
```

### Error Cases:
| HTTP | Reason |
|---|---|
| 400 | `file` missing |
| 400 | Document rejected nahi tha (retry allowed nahi) |
| 400 | 3 attempts ho chuke (contact support) |
| 404 | Document ID nahi mila |

