# Driver App — Login ke baad Screen Routing

## Step 1: Login API call karo
```
POST /api/v1/auth/verify-otp
Body: { phone, otp, role: 'driver' }
```

## Step 2: Response mein `kyc.nextScreen` dekho

```javascript
const { data } = await loginAPI(phone, otp);
const { nextScreen, canGoOnline } = data.kyc;

switch (nextScreen) {
  case 'HOME':
    // KYC complete! Driver home screen pe bhejo
    // canGoOnline = true → Go Online button enable karo
    navigate('DriverHome');
    break;

  case 'KYC_INTRO':
    // Pehli baar — KYC explain karo
    // 6 documents ki list dikhao
    navigate('KycIntroScreen');
    break;

  case 'KYC_UPLOAD':
    // Kuch docs baaki hain
    // GET /kyc/status call karo aur jo 'not_submitted' hai use dikhao
    navigate('KycUploadScreen');
    break;

  case 'KYC_UNDER_REVIEW':
    // Saare docs submit, admin review kar raha hai
    // "We're verifying your documents, usually 24 hours" dikhao
    navigate('KycUnderReviewScreen');
    break;

  case 'KYC_RETRY':
    // Koi doc reject hua
    // GET /kyc/status karo, rejected docs dikhao with rejectionReason
    navigate('KycRetryScreen');
    break;

  case 'ACCOUNT_SUSPENDED':
    // Account suspend — support number dikhao
    navigate('AccountSuspendedScreen');
    break;
}
```

## Step 3: KYC Upload Screen mein
```javascript
// GET /kyc/status call karo
const status = await getKycStatus();

// Documents order (recommended):
const docOrder = ['AADHAAR', 'PAN', 'DRIVING_LICENCE', 'VEHICLE_RC', 'BANK_ACCOUNT', 'SELFIE'];

// Har doc ke liye:
docOrder.forEach(docType => {
  const doc = status.documents.find(d => d.type === docType);

  if (!doc || doc.status === 'not_submitted') {
    // Upload button dikhao
    // SELFIE ke liye: Aadhaar verified hone ke baad hi enable karo
  }

  if (doc?.status === 'auto_verified' || doc?.status === 'approved') {
    // Green tick ✅ dikhao
  }

  if (doc?.status === 'manual_review') {
    // "Under review" ⏳ dikhao
  }

  if (doc?.status === 'rejected') {
    if (doc.canRetry) {
      // Retry button dikhao + rejectionReason message
    } else {
      // "Max retries reached — contact support" dikhao
    }
  }
});

// Overall progress:
// status.verifiedDocsCount / 6 documents
```

## Document Upload — Kaunsa API kab:
| Situation | API |
|---|---|
| Pehli baar upload | POST /kyc/submit |
| Rejected doc dubara | POST /kyc/documents/:id/retry |
| Bank details | POST /kyc/bank (JSON, no file) |
| Selfie | POST /kyc/face-match |

## Status Badge Colors:
| Status | Color | Icon |
|---|---|---|
| `not_submitted` | Grey | Upload icon |
| `pending` | Yellow | Loading spinner |
| `auto_verified` / `approved` | Green | ✅ |
| `manual_review` | Blue | ⏳ Clock |
| `rejected` | Red | ❌ + Retry button |
